dmca.title: German Complaint of Youth Protection and Penal Code Violation (Sec. 184)
dmca.body:
On November 18, 2005, Google received a complaint about webpages that
allegedly violate Section 184 of the German Penal Code and Section 4 of the
Interstate Treaty of Youth Protection in Media
(Jugendmedienschutzstaatsvertrag). In response to this complaint, we have
removed the webpages from www.google.de.
